McGregor has lost one fight, after being on a 100M dollar bender.

He lost to Diaz two weight classes above what his previous fight was, on 8 days notice, and then he beat Diaz in the rematch 2 weight classes above under the same circumstances.

You’d be nuts to think he’s a joke.. realistically he’s lost one fight to Khabib.

McGregor R1 KO over cerrone, back to 155 Motivated, no alcohol, no drugs, he goes on and beats Khabib.
